<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Id like to get an idea of what other people cast when we are in DPS mode.
<br />

<br />
Hypothetical situation:
<br />

<br />
Puller pulls 1 yellow con mob with ^^.
<br />

<br />
Heres my typical casting chain at lvl 42-
<br />

<br />
Despotic Mind, Despair(Melancholy), Muddled Thinking, Liskas Quietude, Despotic Mind, Muddled Thinking, Anguish, Muddled Thinking, Despotic Mind, Muddled Thinking, Despair, Muddled thinking...repeat if its still alive.
<br />

<br />
I know that might be a little hard to read but basically what im doing is casting the big nuke (despotic mind) as soon as it refreshes. In between those refreshes I cast my DOTs very early and weave in a a few mini nukes where i can.
<br />

<br />
What do you guys cast when we are asked to go max DPS?</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
<br />
