<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Basically the same except I start with my DoTs to make sure I dont pull aggro.  In the time it takes to get them off the tank usually esablishes aggro pretty good.
<br />

<br />
Then it is bassically little nuke, little nuke, big nuke, little nuke, little nuke, big nuke...  but I make sure to use my HO every time it pops.  Basically every big nuke is starting a HO.
<br />

<br />
Granted HOs don't add a <span style="font-style: italic">ton</span> but that extra 100-200 damage cant hurt anything.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
